title: Keep That Same Energy
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss Tua Tagovailoa's head injury vs the Bengals and their disappointment in how his situation was been handled by the team and league. We preview a big NFL weekend including some mega QB matchups: Josh Allen vs Lamar Jackson & Patrick Mahomes vs Tom Brady Jalen's confidence in the Lions is sky high this week, AND James Wiseman looks great in his return to the Warriors lineup. All that and more.
